WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Hi everyone, I'm Kirill Danyukov, a 2nd-year student at the Center-College of Applied Qualifications.

2
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.520
I am running for the position of head of the cultural and events committee.

3
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:16.480
Since my school days, I have often participated in various events.

4
00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:22.520
At one point, I attended the Center for the Development of Modern Competencies for Children, where I learned video editing and filming,

5
00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:25.520
as well as how to properly present myself in front of an audience.

6
00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:29.000
After I enrolled at the Center-College of Applied Qualifications,

7
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.800
I started engaging in creative activities, mainly KVN (a comedy team competition show).

8
00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:37.440
At the moment I have my own KVN team, of which I am the leader.

9
00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:43.920
If I become head of the cultural and events committee, I will add the following to my work program.

10
00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:49.400
The first thing I will add is quizzes related to culture, literature, and theater.

11
00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:53.920
The second thing I will add is quests related to one era or another.

12
00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.920
For example, about the culture of the 2000s or the 1990s.

13
00:00:56.920 --> 00:01:01.920
And third, something you will find very interesting — KVN and stand-up comedy.

14
00:01:02.920 --> 00:01:09.920
And the most important question: why should you choose me as head of the cultural and events committee?

15
00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:13.920
First of all, I want to organize events that bring people closer together.

16
00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:21.920
I want to create not just events from the student council, but events that several organizations will work on together.

17
00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:27.920
For example, the Michurinsky Volunteer Corps (MVC), Monolit, and Dvizheniye Pervykh (Movement of the First).

18
00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:34.920
And finally, what I want to say is: protection and support are my duty to the people who voted for me.
